Reasoning: The paper describes a new robotic surgical system for GI surgery, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). The system also involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.MM) for image processing and instrument control. Additionally, the paper discusses the system's force exertion capabilities and instrument dexterity, which relates to mechanical engineering (cs.ME).
